Example 1

In this example swagger description is directly embedded in the page. See source file

/fruits

GET List all fruits

Responses

200 An array of fruits

POST Add a fruit

Parameters

Name Located in Description Type
name body fruit's name String
price body per kilogram fruit's price Float
description body product's description String
origin body product's origin Array of String

Responses

200 Product details
401 Invalid data
403 Insufficient right to add a fruit

/fruits/{id}

GET Fetch a fruit

Responses

200 Fruit details
404 Invalid fruit ID

PUT Update a fruit

Parameters

Name Located in Description Type
name body fruit's name String
price body per kilogram fruit's price Float
description body product's description String
origin body product's origin Array of String

Responses

200 Product details
401 Invalid data

PATCH Partially update a fruit

Parameters

Name Located in Description Type
name body fruit's name String
price body per kilogram fruit's price Float
description body product's description String
origin body product's origin Array of String

Responses

200 Product details
401 Invalid data

DELETE Delete a fruit

Responses

204 Product removed
